{"tid":548148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電暖爐點燃棉被着火　安徽半歲男嬰面部嚴重燒傷　4手指須截肢","createTime":"2018-02-02T08:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T09:12:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b82b975d4326281b5e91f4b6eddf840dd60478c","tid":548148,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"冷風來襲，不少家庭都會用電暖爐取暖，不過使用時要多加小心！安徽宿州蕭縣日前一名不足半歲的男嬰在家午睡時，其嫲嫲開着暖爐後走開，不料暖爐引燃棉被，男嬰面部手部及手部被嚴重燒傷，右手4隻手指更需要做截肢手術，另因為長時間吸入煙塵，其肺部的吸入性損傷亦非常嚴重，目前男嬰仍未度過危險期。<br />\n<br />\n上周六（27日），男嬰在家中午睡，嫲嫲給他蓋好被子，但忘記關掉取暖爐，不料因而點燃被子。當嫲嫲在家門口附近看到屋內冒煙，她趕緊跑回屋內，才發現孫兒睡覺的床起火了。雖然嫲嫲拼命救出男嬰，自己也受了輕傷，但男嬰仍然被燒得面目全非，需緊急送往江蘇徐州仁慈醫院燒傷科進行治療。<br />\n<br />\n經診斷男嬰全身多處燒傷，燒傷部位集中在頭部和面部，及雙耳和手部，而且屬於特重度燒傷，並出現燒傷休克的情況，醫院也發出病危通知書，男嬰目前仍未度過危險期。<br />\n<br />\n更難過的是男嬰右手的4隻手指，因嚴重炭化需要做截肢手術，由於男嬰長時間吸入煙塵，導致孩子的肺部吸入性損傷也非常嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1172620/xlarge/4c71468f541af25927cef98e13ed7108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1172620%2Fxlarge%2F4c71468f541af25927cef98e13ed7108.jpg&h=18c262e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1172630/xlarge/02408e7190e4ed2d502f153ccb536c59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1172630%2Fxlarge%2F02408e7190e4ed2d502f153ccb536c59.jpg&h=ebc7802a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/155680?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F155680%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=Uy%2BW7RV8F6sDBdbTeXJrK9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=90053226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/155680?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"c2ced64b852a8b4cfa52e69fe7cf988c0d9e2fd5","tid":548148,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae7d2d6742ffee255edd200dd6b4050b8110be8","tid":548148,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11a89e8ccd0a9949d30ac9a9dd20548fdf4590d","tid":548148,"uid":76148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"家有一老  如有一寶"},{"pid":"f7cd932968cfd1ff5c0b017b1f3ab20844cc0879","tid":548148,"uid":73910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"仲有半邊臉同唔洗斬手指<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/162730_0dae7f6491bd393afd557b6154f36fe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F162730_0dae7f6491bd393afd557b6154f36fe8.png&h=8d71e5da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93cd0bc56cfba554d14e459a96e4adbdf6adbb77","tid":548148,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7cd932968cfd1ff5c0b017b1f3ab20844cc0879","tid":548148,"uid":73910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"仲有半邊臉同唔洗斬手指<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/02/162730_0dae7f6491bd393afd557b6154f36fe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F162730_0dae7f6491bd393afd557b6154f36fe8.png&h=8d71e5da&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8427e618f76afa7f1abad1d48ee4f8541eb1f691","tid":548148,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f11a89e8